---
---
<section class="relative bg-brand-bg py-20 sm:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl items-center gap-12 px-5 sm:px-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.85fr_1.15fr] lg:gap-16 lg:px-8">
    <div class="reveal relative">
      <div class="relative overflow-hidden border-2 border-brand-secondary/30 shadow-2xl shadow-black/60" style="clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 90%, 90% 100%, 0 100%);">
        <img src="/images/powerhub/home/help.webp" alt="Brian Ho, director of Powerhub Electrical, on site in St Ives" class="h-full w-full object-cover" />
      </div>
      <div class="absolute -bottom-5 -right-3 bg-brand-secondary px-5 py-3 font-heading font-black uppercase text-brand-bg" style="clip-path: polygon(6% 0, 100% 0, 94% 100%, 0 100%);">
        Brian
        <span class="block text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide opacity-80">Founder &amp; Licensed Electrician</span>
      </div>
      <span class="absolute -left-4 top-10 h-24 w-1.5 -skew-y-12 bg-brand-accent"></span>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal" style="transition-delay: 120ms;">
      <p class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-3 font-body text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-brand-muted">
        <span class="inline-block h-px w-10 bg-brand-accent"></span>
        Your St Ives electrician
      </p>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-[clamp(1.9rem,4.5vw,3rem)] font-black uppercase leading-[1.02] tracking-[-0.01em] text-brand-text">
        A personal welcome <span class="text-brand-secondary">from Brian</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-xl font-body text-lg font-medium leading-relaxed text-brand-secondary">
        Licensed electrician, transparent fixed-quote pricing, and a $50 saving on your first service.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-xl font-body text-lg leading-relaxed text-brand-muted">
        I'm Brian, and I started Powerhub Electrical because being the electrician St Ives homeowners actually trust means explaining problems honestly before touching a wire. Whether it's a tripped switchboard or a full rewire, we treat your home like our own.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
